description:
Responsibilities:

Maintain overall aspects of designs and engineering phase, while keeping the product development costs and timelines to market in focus;
Collaborate with cross-functioning team including the US office, design team, project team, suppliers, to ensure multiple projects are being executed according to plan or timeline;
Product Sourcing and cost analysis;
Coordinate, monitor the product design and project implementation;
Responsible for product testing, packing design and package artwork handling.

 Qualification & Requirements:

Degree or above;
2-year experiences in Children toys/Pet Products/Plastic items;
Fresh graduate will be considered;
Strong PC skills and familiar with Project handling;
Knowledge of manufacturing processes and molding processes will be an advantage;
Self-motivated, able to work under pressure, good problem-solving skills;
Good interpersonal & communication skills;
Proficient in spoken & written English and Mandarin;
Occasionally travel to overseas and China;

Responsibilities:

Monitor and follow up orders, shipments and testing;
Handle sample development;

Requirements:

F.7 or above;
At least 1-2 years merchandising experience (manufacturing / trading / buying office), and preferable in garment / toys field;
Good command of English / Mandarin and MS Office software (Excel, Word, PowerPoint & Outlook);
Good communication skill;
Well organize, mature, a good team player and fast learner;
Occasional travel to China;
Immediate available is highly preferable.


We offer attractive competitive package to right candidates.

All related information will be used solely for recruitment purpose and will be destroyed upon completion of recruitment process.

Job Description:

 Responsibilities:

Follow up orders and samples, coordinate with buyer and vendor Mature, self-motivated, able to work under pressure;
Orders follow up to ensure on time delivery;
Work closely and effectively with supporting department including: Production / Marketing / Design & Logistic Team;
Organizational skills and detail oriented is a must;
Assist in ad-hoc assignment as required;
Proactive, out-going and willing to provide problems solving whenever necessary;
General knowledge of material and toy safety regulations;
Fun, young and joyful working environment.

Requirements:

F. 5 / DSE / Diploma holder or above;
At least 2 years’ solid experience in toys industry, more experience will be considered as Merchandiser;
Excellent communication and negotiation skill. Independent and confident in communication with customers and vendors;
Able to work under pressure & good at switching priorities;
Sensitive to figures & number, contains China tax knowledges is a plus;
Excellent command of both written and spoken English, Chinese and Mandarin;
Proficiency in MS Office;
Experience in ERP system;
Willing to PRC travel if necessary

To Apply:

For more information, please visit https://toyzeroplus.com/ .
Interested parties please send your application by “Apply Now”.
All information received will be used for recruitment purpose only and will be kept in strict confidential.

- Degree holder in Marketing or equivalent;

- At least 3 years experience in handling sales & marketing activities such as product development, prepare quotations, samples follow up and orders processing in toys industry;

- Able to work independently and with good self-initiative;

- Demonstrated analytical and negotiation skills;

- Excellent interpersonal and communication skills;

- Proficient in MS Office applications and Chinese Word Processing;

- Good command of written English and Chinese.

Interested candidates, please contact us at 28595011 for company details before applying.

Personal data collected will be used for recruitment purpose only.

